Day 1: Polish the UX 

 Replace text responses with Discord embeds

Price command → Embed with color (green/red), thumbnail
Watchlist → Clean embed with fields for each coin
Alerts list → Formatted embed
Error messages → Red embeds with emoji


 Improve error handling

Handle CoinGecko API rate limits gracefully
Better messages for invalid coins
Handle when user has no DMs enabled (for alerts)


 Add a custom help command

Override default !help
Show all commands with examples
Nice embed format



Day 2: Add Stocks API 

 Install yfinance library (pip install yfinance)
 Create stocks.py file with functions to fetch stock data
 Add stock commands

!stock AAPL - get stock price
!stock TSLA GOOGL NVDA - multiple stocks
Support both crypto and stocks in watchlist
Support stock alerts


 Handle market hours - Show if market is open/closed
 Add stock-specific data - market cap, P/E ratio, volume

